---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Expertise & Experience">
  <section>
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <h1 class="handwritten">Expertise & Experience</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Here is a snapshot of my core capabilities with selected highlights from years
        of research, design, and product work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <!-- Core Expertise -->
      <article class="expertise-section">
        <h2>Core Expertise</h2>
        <ul class="expertise-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Applied User Research & Insight Translation</strong><br>
            Mixed-methods research across AI, voice, telecom, analytics, and enterprise software. Turning ambiguity into clear direction teams can act on.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>AI, Voice, and Conversational Systems</strong><br>
            Designing and validating AI-powered voice experiences, conversation design systems, and LLM interactions.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>0-to-1 and Post-Acquisition Product Strategy</strong><br>
            Shaping early-stage and newly integrated products from problem definition to production across startups, acquisitions, and platform expansions.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Systems Thinking & Data Storytelling</strong><br>
            Breaking down complex systems through clear narratives, frameworks, and visualizations to drive shared understanding.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Collaboration, Facilitation, and Execution</strong><br>
            A hands-on partner to product, design, engineering, and data science teams. Helping teams move forward with confidence.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Mentorship, Teaching, and Workforce Development</strong><br>
            Designing and teaching applied curricula, mentoring students and practitioners, and supporting responsible technology adoption.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Selected Highlights -->
      <article class="expertise-section">
        <h2>Selected Highlights</h2>
        <ul class="expertise-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Defined conversational design standards for AI voice products</strong><br>
            Created a conversation design system guiding zero-to-one AI voice products and helping teams navigate rapid shifts in LLM and voice technology.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Shipped multiple zero-to-one AI and platform products</strong><br>
            Took new products from concept to production by grounding emerging technology in real user needs.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Redesigned global analytics systems under uncertainty</strong><br>
            Rebuilt analytics foundations to ensure statistical integrity, global consistency, and long-term resilience as platforms and data sources evolved.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Led post-acquisition integration research</strong><br>
            Defined integration strategy following Smartsheet's acquisition of 10,000ft by mapping real customer workflows and enabling meaningful cross-product value.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Deep domain expertise in voice, telecom, and hospitality systems</strong><br>
            Conducted extensive research in telecom and voice communications at Hiya and hospitality technology at POSERA, focusing on high-volume, real-time service systems.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Designed and taught applied AI curriculum at the university level</strong><br>
            Co-created and delivered generative AI workshops at the University of Washington, later expanded into a full elective based on student and faculty impact.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .expertise-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .expertise-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .expertise-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .expertise-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .expertise-list li {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
    }

    .expertise-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
